text.tspan: Front panel cutting template for boxcom
1. Cut around border and tape to the front panel
2. Use a center punch to mark the small black circles
3. Use a 1/16-inch drill to make pilot holes
5. Drill 0.125-inch diameter holes with a multi-diameter drill
6. Drill 0.5-inch diameter holes with a multi-diameter drill
7. Use a nibbler to remove the rectangle
3 x 3 inch cutout in BUD box
